  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Dialog: Function-Block: Linear-Motion</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2" style="page-break-before:always;">Linear-Motion FB </para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-AddFBLinearMotion">Add Linear-Motion FB</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The default output from the <text styleclass="Element-Header">Linear-Motion FB</text> is equal to the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Master-Machine-Angle" styleclass="Interface">Master-Machine-Angle (MMA)</link><text styleclass="Interface">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Use the <text styleclass="Element">Linear-Motion dialog</text> to advance or delay the output relative to the <text styleclass="Interface">Master-Machine-Angle</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="Element">Linear-Motion FB</text> does not have an input-connector. </para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_" style="text-indent:-36px; margin-left:36px;"><image src="tog_plus.gif" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image><tab /><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="tog_plus.gif" src-expanded="tog_minus.gif"><caption><![CDATA[How to open the Linear-Motion dialog-box]]></caption><title>Click to exapand /collapse</title></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:110px; border-right:none;">
          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="MD-LinearMotionFB-GA.ipp" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="-99.90%" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td style="border-left:none;">
          <para styleclass="Body Table">To open the<text styleclass="Element"> Linear-Motion dialog</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="border-top:none; border-right:none; border-bottom:none;">
                <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets">Double-click the </text><text styleclass="Element">Linear-Motion FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets"> in </text><text styleclass="Body Text">the graphics-area</text><text styleclass="VariableName">. </text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Interface2">OR</para>
                <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-How-to-Open-a-Dialog-Box" styleclass="SeeAlso">How to Open a dialog</link><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="Element-Header">Linear-Motion dialog</text> is now open.</para>
